This directory is used for the airfield files.

KFLog supports two different airfield sources:

1. WELT2000. The latest file is to find here:

   http://www.segelflug.de/vereine/welt2000/download/WELT2000.TXT

   More information about WELT2000 is available at:

   http://www.segelflug.de/vereine/welt2000/

2. openAIP airfields from http://www.openaip.net/. See there
   for more information.

KFLog downloads airfield files automatically for you in the settings
airfields page. Please define on that page, which airfield source
(Welt2000 or openAIP) do you want to use and for which countries airfield
data should be loaded.
